title: Middlekauff – 3 & Out – Warriors/Patriots culture parallels; Bad look for Le'Veon; Dallas should wait to pay Dak; Mailbag
itunes:title: Middlekauff – 3 & Out – Warriors/Patriots culture parallels; Bad look for Le'Veon; Dallas should wait to pay Dak; Mailbag
description:
Subscribe here to the 3 and Out with John Middlekauff Podcast https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/3-and-out-with-john-middlekauff/id1352730623?mt=2. In this episode, Middlekauff looks at the similarities between Warriors and Patriots' cultures, why Le'Veon Bell missing Jets mini camp is a terrible look, why Dallas shouldn't be in a hurry to pay Dak, and answers listener questions in a post-NFL Draft Middlekauff's Mailbag. Follow John on twitter @JohnMiddlekauff and go to www.theherdnow.com to find the latest content. Subscribe now!
